505
00:52:22,489 --> 00:52:25,856
<i> Joseph! Joe. </i>

506
00:52:27,994 --> 00:52:30,292
Holy shit.
Come on.

507
00:52:41,708 --> 00:52:43,642
Turn it off.

508
00:52:43,710 --> 00:52:46,838
Turn it off!

509
00:52:46,913 --> 00:52:49,643
I've been trying to keep you conscious.

510
00:52:51,251 --> 00:52:54,516
- Where are we going?
