00:59:08,928 --> 00:59:12,193
Told you I was working a case.

599
00:59:12,265 --> 00:59:15,598
Why do you keep lying
to me, Joseph?

600
00:59:15,668 --> 00:59:18,398
You cannot keep doing this.
We...

601
00:59:18,471 --> 00:59:20,996
Oh, my God.
What happened to you?

602
00:59:21,074 --> 00:59:24,407
<i>I got jumped by a couple of guys,</i>
<i>but I'm all right. </i>

603
00:59:24,477 --> 00:59:28,641
Daddy, are you home yet?

604
00:59:28,715 --> 00:59:33,652
No, sweetheart, I'm just... I'm here for
a little while, and then I gotta go.

605
00:59:33,720 --> 00:59:36,018
Come in here
with me.

606
00:59:36,089 --> 00:59:39,490
- When are you coming home?
- Shh.

607
00:59:39,559 --> 00:59:43,393
Sweetie, just go back to sleep.

608
01:00:21,266 --> 01:00:23,700
It's okay.

609
01:00:59,938 --> 01:01:01,997
Hello?

610
01:01:02,074 --> 01:01:04,668
<i>Hi. How are you?</i>

611
01:01:07,379 --> 01:01:10,371
<i>Wait!</i>
<i>Hello?</i>

612
01:01:10,449 --> 01:01:12,383
<i>Hello?</i>

613
01:01:14,753 --> 01:01:17,586
<i>That was your mother. </i>

614
01:01:17,656 --> 01:01:20,989
- What?
