615
01:01:21,059 --> 01:01:24,290
<i>Someone that you were looking for,</i>
<i>or something like that?</i>

616
01:01:24,363 --> 01:01:28,129
I think that she said he was
some kind of engineer.

617
01:01:33,071 --> 01:01:35,665
I don't want you
to leave this house.

618
01:01:35,741 --> 01:01:38,403
Do you understand me?

619
01:01:40,712 --> 01:01:43,647
I want you to lock all the doors
