01:03:34,960 --> 01:03:37,554
What a fine-looking boy.

641
01:04:03,155 --> 01:04:06,249
<i>Mom, you guys okay?</i>

642
01:04:06,324 --> 01:04:08,258
<i>Why don't you</i>
<i>visit us, Joe?</i>

