662
01:07:09,007 --> 01:07:10,941
Sir? Sir, wait!

663
01:07:11,009 --> 01:07:12,943
That man had a gun!

664
01:07:18,316 --> 01:07:20,750
<i></i>
<i>Don't you fuckin'move!</i>

